    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/credibility-assessment-team-depuy",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All three QoIs satisfy the pre-established acceptance bounds (E/uval < 1.96, percent difference < 10%). Twelve of thirteen credibility factors meet or exceed required levels. The single shortfall (Test conditions, achieved 2 vs. required 3) is mitigated by the strong quantitative agreement across all QoIs and the direct correspondence between validation and COU scenarios. The overall credibility evidence is sufficient to support regulatory submission for the non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw design.",
